75b","tid":392363,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"自己拎黎柒"},{"pid":"eb1d7c899626164e404f824b4e10953b54a98290","tid":392363,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"因為一單自殺而引發學生群起抗爭對付強權<br />\n蔡氏長子真烈士也 願安息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe853a473a005ae924d0295cd029288b06f2706","tid":392363,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"cheng lap: 甲欺負乙，乙反擊，懲罰乙。乙不反擊，則要對甲的欺負視而不見。盡量找出甲的可憐之處，勸所有同學容忍甲，再找乙一個錯誤來放大，鼓勵同學批鬥乙。<br />\n<br />\n呢班掌權既死老野,對土共既批鬥全部視而不見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b94ec10faa6c1f73d53a446dcbe70f94724166","tid":392363,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發夢夢見教院前幾年搵人reg day影相之後send比報紙屌學生組織 而且年年都咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係真<br />\n咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我相有機會係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有眼睇<br />\n而家做教育既人幾賤格"},{"pid":"82a9811bf75b2f12b263c1cad2e025516f2fa3ab","tid":392363,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"教育局專搵弱智做局長就知咩事啦"}]}